 > On the contrary, I think it's very valuable to get students to
 > understand that what they *want* to write is
 >
 > (: all ((%a -> %b) (list-of %a) -> (list-of %b)))
 >
 > but all they *can* write is
 >
 > (: all ((Any -> Any) (list-of Any) -> (list-of Any)))
